  dataanalyzer.entity.Sequence<Data,java.util.ArrayList<Data>>

IInformation, java.io.Serializable
public class SequenceData
extends Sequence<Data,java.util.ArrayList<Data>>
implements java.io.Serializable, IInformation

An implementation of the Sequence sequence class using the Data class as the unit and an ArrayList as the container.
